---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Neon Injector"
  description="Learn how Neon Injector collects, uses, and protects your personal information to ensure your privacy."
>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <main class="flex-1 pt-16">
      <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-[var(--text-color)]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neon-purple mb-8 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <p class="mb-4">At Neon Injector, your privacy is a top priority. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information to provide a secure and transparent experience.</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Contact Information</strong>: Name and email provided through our contact form.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: Anonymous data on app interactions to improve functionality.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information</strong>: OS version, device model, and other technical details for compatibility.</li>
          </ul>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>To process support requests and respond to inquiries.</li>
            <li>To analyze usage trends and optimize Neon Injectorâ€™s performance.</li>
            <li>To send occasional updates about new features or skins (opt-in only).</li>
          </ul>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">3. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties, except:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>As required by law or legal processes.</li>
            <li>To protect the rights, property, or safety of Neon Injector and its users.</li>
          </ul>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">4. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We use industry-standard encryption and secure servers to protect your data. However, no online system is 100% secure, and users should exercise caution when sharing sensitive information.</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">5. Your Rights</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Request access to or deletion of your personal data.</li>
            <li>Opt out of any email communications.</li>
            <li>Contact us for any privacy concerns at <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">support@neon-injector.my.id</a>.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">This policy was last updated on June 10, 2025. For questions, please visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact</a> page.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>